comment.body:
I'd recommend using the inline style to set a CSS variable and consume it in your style.

```tsx
const FivePrinter = styled.div.attrs(p => ({style: {...p.style, '--sc-color-even': p.$colorEven}}))<{ $colorEven: string; }>`
  tr:nth-child(even) {
    background-color: var(--sc-color-even);
  }
`; 
```

